Usage:

    waveform [options]

    Available options with their defaults:
    --in audiofile              (required)
    --out pngfile               (required)
    --width 256                 height of the image
    --width 64                  width of the image
    --color-bg 00000000         bg color, rrggbbaa
    --color-center 000000ff     gradient center color, rrggbbaa
    --color-outer 000000ff      gradient outer color, rrggbbaa

Dependencies:

    libsndfile
    libpng
    zlib

Compile:

    gcc -o waveform main.c -lsndfile -lz -lpng

